<br />\n其實職業治療番譯得唔好，職業治療(Occupational Therapy)嘅occupation唔係淨係指工作/職業，而係包括所有對人有意義嘅活動(meaningful activities)。 <br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲activities可以係self-care activities (eating, showering, dressing, walking), leisure activities (打機，買野，上網，畫畫), social activities (交友，出街，約會拍拖), rest 等等。當然工作都係meaningful activities。<br />\n<br />\n而OT就係幫人去解決做唔到呢啲activities 嘅困難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7a00d9309e69925ab3dc4f6f77719450a1deb6","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1c6fcb79788a41ffc5cb92dedb5c2e3efacebc3f","tid":2119100,"uid":140666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d82a32d2ab1bbf2656434f792d5434bd1e2aa1","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f91a3a6a3a91d625f721e266139b1eb4bba50701","tid":2119100,"uid":96533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"做咗<br />\n好好奇點解OT 會研究dating<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"Thanks Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個問題好多人都有問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我幫職業治療界宣傳下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實職業治療番譯得唔好，職業治療(Occupational Therapy)嘅occupation唔係淨係指工作/職業，而係包括所有對人有意義嘅活動(meaningful activities)。 <br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲activities可以係self-care activities (eating, showering, dressing, walking), leisure activities (打機，買野，上網，畫畫), social activities (交友，出街，約會拍拖), rest 等等。當然工作都係meaningful activities。<br />\n<br />\n而OT就係幫人去解決做唔到呢啲activities 嘅困難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:50:44.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係dating 有困難都可以搵OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd26e225a3cad1e1660fc5c155e81c5ed96ef06","tid":2119100,"uid":34514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"填咗<br />\n多謝樓主俾我回憶多一次, 特別係我人生第一次date<br />\n雖然始終冇結果, 但係一段美好回憶嚟<br />\n<br />\n另外, 都借個位<br />\n[警世 你問我答] 絶對唔好入城大材料工程 materials engineering!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121835</a>"},{"pid":"a97a0fb7221199570f19a00fd1e7ee0c04896738","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6fcb79788a41ffc5cb92dedb5c2e3efacebc3f","tid":2119100,"uid":140666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d82a32d2ab1bbf2656434f792d5434bd1e2aa1","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f91a3a6a3a91d625f721e266139b1eb4bba50701","tid":2119100,"uid":96533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"做咗<br />\n好好奇點解OT 會研究dating<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"Thanks Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個問題好多人都有問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我幫職業治療界宣傳下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實職業治療番譯得唔好，職業治療(Occupational Therapy)嘅occupation唔係淨係指工作/職業，而係包括所有對人有意義嘅活動(meaningful activities)。 <br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲activities可以係self-care activities (eating, showering, dressing, walking), leisure activities (打機，買野，上網，畫畫), social activities (交友，出街，約會拍拖), rest 等等。當然工作都係meaningful activities。<br />\n<br />\n而OT就係幫人去解決做唔到呢啲activities 嘅困難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:50:44.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係dating 有困難都可以搵OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"我諗dating暫時係OT入面都唔係好popular<br />\n不過呢個研究絕對幫到所有了解究竟現今大家GE理想對象係點, 點樣先可以initiate同你心儀GE人下齊GE 機會, etc.<br />\n唔排除將來專做呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cd3b1bf8241cca3c4e4cc6a10692702b8b9fa8","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cd26e225a3cad1e1660fc5c155e81c5ed96ef06","tid":2119100,"uid":34514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"填咗<br />\n多謝樓主俾我回憶多一次, 特別係我人生第一次date<br />\n雖然始終冇結果, 但係一段美好回憶嚟<br />\n<br />\n另外, 都借個位<br />\n[警世 你問我答] 絶對唔好入城大材料工程 materials engineering!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121835</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:46:01.000Z","msg":"Thanks Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb8cc3cdf4d19e638208fb1d16c00c5fe99b10b","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e258890b16d4fd587a70136ac6df69e06e5d10fd","tid":2119100,"uid":201890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"J圖做問卷"},{"pid":"d5a18d756b4520837ca8bae29a7f86840b9c0fab","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"69392cce3729bf64e7d88f9256555a14d5568001","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T00:49:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"95e0b9f078ccedec679a4598883965791eda9a04","tid":2119100,"uid":90532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"原來都幾長下 做份野諗起好多以前既野 做做下做左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw加油<br />\n想問下你讀degree定master"},{"pid":"8ab12b5b11deb7d329c71a413d3ccc3127c5ed56","tid":2119100,"uid":117366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e0b9f078cced