ation). 舉個例有位有disability ge Ching想約個女仔出街食飯, 有咩可以做?<br />\n<strong>Person: </strong> Build up capacity(e.g. social skills. communication skills, confidence, physical capacity, etc.)<br />\n<strong>Environment:</strong> Equipment prescription (for mobility? modified cutlery? communication devices? assistive technology), 揀咩類型GE餐廳 (wheelchair accessible?)wheelchair accessible?), social environemnt? physical environment?<br />\n<strong>Occupation:</strong> 可以點樣改變約會GE型式去令到Ching參與到? 例如一位ching想整個甜品溝女, 但又唔識煮 &gt;&gt; 用現成cake mix? 研究一D合乎佢capacity整到GE 甜品等等<br />\nsorry for 1999, 冇真實GE case, 亦冇咩人真實做過相關clinical practice~我只能用有限知識解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}